#2266
The Collapsed Entrance~
You stand at the edge of a massive collapse, where the mountainside has crumbled inward to reveal a dark tunnel descending into the earth.  Broken timbers and shattered stone litter the path leading down.  A faint cold wind rises from below, carrying the smell of old dust and something faintly magical.
