#2267
The Outer Corridor~
A long corridor stretches before you, its arched ceiling blackened by old fire. The walls are carved stone, etched with the remains of murals depicting a great order of mages at the height of their power.  Most of the murals are defaced or worn beyond recognition, but a few fragments remain.
