#2268
The Hall of Shattered Pillars~
The hall was once grand, supported by enormous pillars of carved marble. Most of them have toppled, and their fragments create a maze of obstacles across the floor.  Ash drifts in lazy spirals from above.  Something moved behind one of the fallen columns just a moment ago.
