The Charred Armoury~
This was once the sanctum's armoury.  Fire has gutted it completely, leaving only blackened racks and melted weapon frames behind.  The heat here is still faintly detectable even after all these years.  A few Flamebound Sentinels appear to have been created here, and never left.
