The Sentinels' Watch~
A wide chamber that once served as a guard post.  Recessed alcoves line the walls where the Flamebound Sentinels presumably stood at rest.  The floor is cracked and warped from decades of intense magical heat.  The door to the south is massive, reinforced iron -- and locked.
