#2275
The Riddlegolem's Chamber~
A perfectly square room, its floor inlaid with concentric rings of carved runes.  At the centre sits the Riddlegolem, an ancient construct whose purpose was to test would-be entrants to the inner sanctum.  The northern exit is sealed by a magical barrier that shimmers and wavers like heat haze.
